pageContext.claim: “Jon Tester led the Democrat mob in the effort to destroy the reputation of a great man, Admiral Ronny Jackson.”
pageContext.analysis: Tester led the public charge against the Jackson nomination to run the Department of Veterans Affairs and released a memo that contained unverified claims against the Jackson, based on interviews of people who worked with Jackson. But Trump ignores the fact many Republicans believed Jackson to be unqualified and that Tester's actions had the support of the Veterans Affairs Committee chairman, Johnny Isakson (R-Ga.)
